data.description: Welcome to this charming two-bedroom and two and a half bathroom condo in the beautiful Eastlake community. The generously proportioned living room captivates with its cozy  fireplace, adding warmth and character to the space.  This condo unit is walking distance to shopping, restaurants and top rated school in South Bay area. The cute patio has enough room for a barbecue grill. The master bedroom has a walk in closet closet and attic to store your valuable belongings and the other bedroom has a full bathroom. Close to freeway exit.
